  ],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In order to provide a load distribution amongst different partitions (cores),"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "the main threads of execution in the COM module, namely the respective MainFunctions are assigned to different partitions."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The general concept for the multipartition support of the COM is, that the ComIPdus are processed in the MainFunction which is referenced via the ComIPduMainFunctionRef."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Main Functions are assigned to a partition via the ComMainTx/Rx/RouteSignalsPartitionRef. Additionally, the ComIPdus are assigned to a partition via the “global” Pdu which defined in EcuC."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Zeekr need implement multicore COM on core0 and core1. All the flexRay PDUs should be process on core1, for CAN and Lin Pdus should be process on core0."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "/confluence/download/attachments/2754792481/Multicore%20COM%20stack.png?version=8&modificationDate=1701395142000&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/Multicore COM stack.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Initialization and Deinitialization"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The COM shares all RAM between partitions, due to that the Com_Init() and Com_DeInit() functions must only be called once to initialize/deinitialize the COM variables."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Zeekr call Com_Init() on core0."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Com main function configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Create main functions and assign to EcucPartition_QM_Core0 and EcucPartition_QM_Core1."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Assign them to BSWTask_5ms_Core0 and BSWTask_5ms_Core1 in OS."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-2-28_10-30-38.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-2-28_10-30-38.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Com Ipdu configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "FlexRay ComIPdus should reference ComMainFunctionTx_Core1 and ComMainFunctionRx_Core1."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "CAN Lin ComIPdus should reference ComMainFunctionTx_Core0 and ComMainFunctionRx_Core0."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-2-28_10-49-13.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-2-28_10-49-13.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-2-28_10-46-17.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-2-28_10-46-17.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "ECUC need assign global PDU to different partition"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Global pdu should assign to EcucPartition_QM_Core0 and EcucPartition_QM_Core1."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step4"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Signal Routings and Description Routings are only supported “partition local”. This can't match the customer requirement."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I deleted GW mapping locally."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-2-28_11-52-4.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-2-28_11-52-4.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "PDUR configuration."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-3-13_14-21-10.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-3-13_14-21-10.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "PDUR shared ram should be assigned in MemMap module."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-3-1_10-22-17.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-3-1_10-22-17.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-3-1_15-46-42.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-3-1_15-46-42.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-3-1_15-15-18.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-3-1_15-15-18.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": ".OS_OsApplication_QM_Core1_VAR_NOINIT needed, but no define in ld file."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Rte configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Set RteOptimizationMode from MEMORY to RUNTIME."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM/image2023-2-28_12-10-45.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM/image2023-2-28_12-10-45.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step7"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The ports between Com and Rte need to check."
    },
